Return to Kuttenberg and take over a burnt-down forge where Henry's father once worked as an apprentice. Legacy of The Forge, the second story DLC for Kingdom Come: Deliverance II, is out now.
 
Meet new characters, uncover the truth behind a long-lost masterpiece Henry's father once worked on, and turn the ruined forge into your own fully customisable home - with over 100 million ways to design your workshop, surroundings, and private quarters. Earn your place as a true master blacksmith, one job at a time.
 
Legacy of The Forge is out now on PlayStation 5.

Is Bubsy a celebrated icon from the mascot wars of the early 90s or a platforming punchline? Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection explores the franchise's troubled history and enduring popularity. What could possibly go wrong?

Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection is a playable history that includes games, artifacts and interviews. All of the games have been carefully updated for modern platforms with features such as enhanced resolution and framerate along with save states and rewind functionality.
